SD=Consumer Loan
CR= Consumer Loan Fulfillment Arrangement
BQs=Interest ServiceFees Disbursement Maintenance Withdrawal Repayment Restructuring
The consumer loan product may include different properties/features depending on a bank's preferences and policies. The loan is targeted at consumer customer and may be associated with a type of product and may or may not be secured by collateral.
"A consumer customer applies for and gets a loan to purchase new furniture."
This service domain handles the fulfillment of a consumer loan product. This includes the initial set-up of the loan facility and the completion of scheduled and ad-hoc product processing tasks
CR - Consumer Loan Fulfillment Arrangement				BQ 1 - Interest	BQ 2 - Service Fees		BQ 3 - Disbursement	BQ 4 - Maintenance		BQ 5 - Withdrawal				BQ 6 - Repayment				BQ 7 - Restructuring				
In	Up	Co	Re	Re	Ex	Re	Re	Rq	Re	Up	Ex	Rq	Re	Up	Ex	Rq	Re	In	Up	Ec	Rq	Re
Initiate a consumer loan
Update details for an existing consumer loan
Control a consumer loan (e.g. suspend, terminate)
Retrieve details about a consumer loan
Retrieve details about interest applied to a consumer loan
Execute a fee charge against a consumer loan
Retrieve details about a consumer loan fees
Retrieve details about a disbursement paid against a consumer loan
Request a maintenance activity for a consumer load (e.g. obtain a fee statement)
Retrieve details about maintenance processing for a consumer loan
Update details of a withdrawal from a consumer loan
Execute an automated withdrawal against a consumer loan
Request handling of a withdrawal (e.g. negotiate an exception)
Retrieve details about a consumer loan withdrawal
Update a repayment transaction made to the consumer loan
Execute an automated repayment transaction
Request handling of an exceptional repayment (e.g. a balloon repayment)
Retrieve details about a consumer loan repayment
Initiate consumer loan account restructuring
Update details of a consumer loan or restructuring activities
Accept, reject etc a consumer loan restructuring proposal
Request activity associated with a restructuring effort (e.g. negotiate)
Retrieve details about a consumer loan restructuring task